  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001370.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For An , king of all lands , and Inana , lady of the E-ana , Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu , king of Kiš ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001370.5",
      "line_range": "5",
      "translation": "(5) After Inana combined the title of en and the title of king for Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu , he ruled as en in Unug , while he ruled as king in Urim ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001370.15",
      "line_range": "15",
      "translation": "(15) When Inana blessed Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu , Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu dedicated this ( vessel ) to Inana , his lady for his ( own ) well-being ."
    }
  ],
